.TH HYPRLAND\-DIALOG 1 "2025-11-20" "hyprland-guiutils 0.2.1" "Hyprland Ecosystem"
.SH NAME
hyprland\-dialog \- display a dialog window for Hyprland
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B hyprland\-dialog
.RI [ options ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B hyprland\-dialog
is a GUI dialog utility for the Hyprland ecosystem.
It displays a dialog window with a title, text content, and configurable
buttons.
When a button is clicked, its label is printed to standard output and the
dialog closes.
.PP
The window class is
.BR hyprland\-dialog .
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BI \-\-title " string"
Set the dialog title, displayed as a heading.
.TP
.BI \-\-apptitle " string"
Set the window/application title.
.TP
.BI \-\-text " string"
Set the dialog body text.
Supports
.B <br/>
and
.B \en
for line breaks.
.TP
.BI \-\-buttons " string"
Semicolon\-separated list of button labels
(e.g.\&
.IR "\(dqOK;Cancel;Help\(dq" ).
.SH EXAMPLES
Display a confirmation dialog:
.PP
.RS
.nf
result=$(hyprland\-dialog \-\-title "Confirm" \e
    \-\-text "Are you sure?" \e
    \-\-buttons "Yes;No")
.fi
.RE
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR Hyprland (1)
.SH AUTHOR
The Hyprland Development Team
.SH BUGS
Report bugs at
.UR https://github.com/hyprwm/hyprland-guiutils/issues
.UE .
